==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''to hydrogenate'''
#{{chemistry}} to [[treat]] something, or [[react]] something, with [[hydrogen]]; especially to react an [[unsaturated fat]] with hydrogen, in the presence of a [[nickel]] [[catalyst]], to produce a harder [[saturated fat]]
